outputs.output_descr: The programme aims at contributing to the economic and social development of Kuwait, with a particular focus on empowerment of Kuwaiti women, by addressing the problem of unemployment among women. Unleashing their entrepreneurial potential, the programme will support the establishment and growth of enterprises, owned/managed by women, thereby providing employment opportunities for self and others. In doing so, the programme will develop and strengthen national institutional capacities in order to sustain the programme in the long run.

project_title: Economic Empowerment of Kuwaiti Women Project
